snippet.title: Breakout: The Dark Prison Trailer 2019 (Android/iOS)
snippet.description:
The blockbuster 3D game is under development right now.
Here is the trailer for players to have a taste. Enjoy!

FEATURES OF THE GAME:
- the Best AAA grade Action RPG on iOS and Android
- Support realtime PVP, Co-op and PVE
- Unique control and gameplay on mobile
- Strong full 3D graphic and animation
- Over 400 items and equipments for players to change their outlook and costumes
- Specially designed Monster and Zombies for real challenge!

Breakout: The Dark Prison is now ready for pre-registration in Google Play Store. Come and prepare for toughest rescue mission now! 

Google Play Store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.latersoft.darkprison

App Store (iOS):
Coming Soon!
